{"tid":1724939,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"公務員被捕就即時停職","createTime":"2019-11-15T15:09:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T16:30:50.000Z","uid":338591,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c133d53be24e01734b57e0640cece090fe0b3cc5","tid":1724939,"uid":338591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:09:46.000Z","msg":"公務員被捕就即時停職，唔係落charge先停職。<br />\n<br />\n有關公墓猿被捕就即時停職，睇下前局長王永平點講：<br />\n<br />\n個別公務員在面對刑事訴訟或紀律研訊期間，當局如認為有關人員在未裁定無罪之前繼續執行職務並不符合公眾利益，可飭令他停職（即暫時停止執行職務）。<br />\n <br />\n我們不會輕率採取停職措施。在作出停職決定前，我們會考慮的因素包括：有關人員被控的刑事罪行或違紀行為的性質和嚴重程度；他如果獲准繼續執行職務，可能再犯同類不當行為的機會有多大；暫時將他調往其他職位是否可行；以及公眾的看法。只有在把該員調往其他職位並不可行或不合適時，我們才會採用停職措施。<br />\n<br />\n醬油：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.csb.gov.hk/tc_chi/info/1028.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.csb.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Finfo%2F1028.html&d=NKgE6Majit0rEYuBm%2F0CvlhCriQ9KcwZROA2Rh0I8Zw%3D&h=8b191fbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.csb.gov.hk/tc_chi/info/1028.html</a>"},{"pid":"d67efc7f141fc113c17da03ea7c465f0e0d51ee9","tid":1724939,"uid":32352,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:10:56.000Z","msg":"交通警撞人停職未？"},{"pid":"062e81eeaa6a8c8a9fc59ffef93f028886544a8b","tid":1724939,"uid":190793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:13:54.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n韓國戰線要人呀！！完全冇人簽<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6be34d833660fb86a736d07dc7a4bace302bcd3a","tid":1724939,"uid":261913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d67efc7f141fc113c17da03ea7c465f0e0d51ee9","tid":1724939,"uid":32352,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:10:56.000Z","msg":"交通警撞人停職未？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:15:51.000Z","msg":"等緊拎大紫荊啦 <br />\n停職？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9a6957d2ef19a095f17737